StopPlace

Description of each stop, including accessibility, address, and parking features

get_stopPlaces(operator_id, stop_id = NA)

Arguments

operator_id

Operator ID is used to filter the request
stop_id

ID identifying the stop

Value

Dataframe of stops, columns are characteristics of stops

Examples

get_stopPlaces(operator_id='AC')
#> [1] 200
